Node unit tests
-------------------------
To run tests:
mocha .\test\**\*.js

To debug tests:
node-debug -p 8090 _mocha .\test\**\*.js --no-timeouts

Node integration tests
-------------------------
To run tests:
mocha .\integration-test\**\*.js

To debug tests:
node-debug -p 8090 _mocha .\integration-test\**\*.js --no-timeouts